      "span_text": "Data from microarray studies in the Oncomine database [CITATION_1] showed that these hypomethylated genes were, in general, overexpressed at the mRNA level in prostate cancers compared with benign prostate and that the overexpression was often more pronounced in metastatic prostate cancers than in primary prostate cancers (Supplementary Fig. S4 )."
